The '''''African Journal of Ecology''''' (formerly ''East African Wildlife Journal'') is a quarterly scientific journal focused on the ecology and conservation of the animals and plants of Africa. It is published by [[Wiley-Blackwell|Blackwell Publishing]] in association with the [[East African Wildlife Society]].
